videos.headline: Knowles goes 70 yards to the house
videos.description: Skylar Thompson finds Malik Knowles and he goes untouched for a 70-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Knowles goes 70 yards to the house) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson hits Schoen for clutch 3rd-down conversion
videos.description: Skylar Thompson finds Dalton Schoen on the drag route and he goes 21 yards up the field.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Thompson hits Schoen for clutch 3rd-down conversion) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gill comes down with juggling TD
videos.description: Skylar Thompson hits Wykeen Gill on the corner route for the 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Gill comes down with juggling TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' flea flicker turns into 21-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger fools the defense with a flea flicker and hits Collin Johnson for a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Texas' flea flicker turns into 21-yard TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ingram slices through K-State defense for 34-yard TD
videos.description: Keaontay Ingram blazes his way through the defense and dives into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Ingram slices through K-State defense for 34-yard TD) 2019/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dicker's chip shot lifts Texas as time expires
videos.description: Cameron Dicker hits a 26-yard field goal as time expires as the Longhorns go on to defeat the Wildcats.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Dicker's chip shot lifts Texas as time expires) 2019/11/09 ESHEET
